title: American Illustrator Art - Identification and Price Guide
description:
House of Collectibles | 1991 | ISBN: 0876378335 | English | 348 pages | PDF | 38 MB


From printed magazine covers to record album jackets to book illustrations, the market for illustrator art has skyrocketed, and collector interest has reached an all-time high. The Official Price Guide to American Illustrator Art is the one reference every level of collector can turn to for up-to-the-minute information
